body:
Comment 24: 
VERSION.cache should not have "go.tools" in it. Mine has "devel +9e46fca8567b Mon Jul 29
12:08:19 2013 +1000". I cannot think of why yours get go.tools in it. But it should not
be difficult to determine. cmd/dist writes into the file, so if you use xprintf in
cmd/dist to print what is happening step by step, you should be able to determine what
is wrong. Please, have a go and report back here.

Thank you.

Alex
